{
  "video_id": "o3oDpCb7VqI",
  "title": "Maryn McKenna: What do we do when antibiotics donâ€™t work any more?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12921.0,
      "end_time": 14918.0,
      "text": "This is my great uncle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14918.0,
      "end_time": 17936.0,
      "text": "my father&#39;s father&#39;s younger brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17936.0,
      "end_time": 20142.0,
      "text": "His name was Joe McKenna."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20142.0,
      "end_time": 25089.0,
      "text": "He was a young husband and a semi-pro basketball player"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25089.0,
      "end_time": 29407.0,
      "text": "and a fireman in New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29407.0,
      "end_time": 32007.0,
      "text": "Family history says he loved being a fireman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32006.999999999996,
      "end_time": 35542.0,
      "text": "and so in 1938, on one of his days off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35542.0,
      "end_time": 39019.0,
      "text": "he elected to hang out at the firehouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39019.0,
      "end_time": 43218.0,
      "text": "To make himself useful that day, he started polishing all the brass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43218.0,
      "end_time": 46612.0,
      "text": "the railings on the fire truck, the fittings on the walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46612.0,
      "end_time": 48957.0,
      "text": "and one of the fire hose nozzles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48957.0,
      "end_time": 51465.0,
      "text": "a giant, heavy piece of metal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51465.0,
      "end_time": 55574.0,
      "text": "toppled off a shelf and hit him."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55574.0,
      "end_time": 59382.0,
      "text": "A few days later, his shoulder started to hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59382.0,
      "end_time": 62656.0,
      "text": "Two days after that, he spiked a fever."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62656.0,
      "end_time": 65141.0,
      "text": "The fever climbed and climbed."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65141.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67091.0,
      "text": "His wife was taking care of him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67091.0,
      "end_time": 71393.0,
      "text": "but nothing she did made a difference, and when they got the local doctor in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71393.0,
      "end_time": 74149.0,
      "text": "nothing he did mattered either."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74149.0,
      "end_time": 77911.0,
      "text": "They flagged down a cab and took him to the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77911.0,
      "end_time": 81905.0,
      "text": "The nurses there recognized right away that he had an infection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81905.0,
      "end_time": 86061.0,
      "text": "what at the time they would have called &quot;blood poisoning,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86061.0,
      "end_time": 88174.0,
      "text": "and though they probably didn&#39;t say it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88174.0,
      "end_time": 90031.0,
      "text": "they would have known right away"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90031.0,
      "end_time": 93770.0,
      "text": "that there was nothing they could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93770.0,
      "end_time": 96788.0,
      "text": "There was nothing they could do because the things we use now"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96788.0,
      "end_time": 99737.0,
      "text": "to cure infections didn&#39;t exist yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99737.0,
      "end_time": 103173.0,
      "text": "The first test of penicillin, the first antibiotic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103173.0,
      "end_time": 105843.0,
      "text": "was three years in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105843.0,
      "end_time": 110547.0,
      "text": "People who got infections either recovered, if they were lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110547.0,
      "end_time": 112322.0,
      "text": "or they died."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112322.0,
      "end_time": 114411.0,
      "text": "My great uncle was not lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114411.0,
      "end_time": 117708.0,
      "text": "He was in the hospital for a week, shaking with chills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117708.0,
      "end_time": 119566.0,
      "text": "dehydrated and delirious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119566.0,
      "end_time": 122468.0,
      "text": "sinking into a coma as his organs failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122468.0,
      "end_time": 124604.0,
      "text": "His condition grew so desperate"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124604.0,
      "end_time": 129234.0,
      "text": "that the people from his firehouse lined up to give him transfusions"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129234.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133497.0,
      "text": "hoping to dilute the infection surging through his blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133497.0,
      "end_time": 137143.0,
      "text": "Nothing worked. He died."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137143.0,
      "end_time": 140115.0,
      "text": "He was 30 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 140115.0,
      "end_time": 142088.0,
      "text": "If you look back through history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142088.0,
      "end_time": 145362.0,
      "text": "most people died the way my great uncle died."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145362.0,
      "end_time": 148032.0,
      "text": "Most people didn&#39;t die of cancer or heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148032.0,
      "end_time": 152490.0,
      "text": "the lifestyle diseases that afflict us in the West today."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152490.0,
      "end_time": 156229.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t die of those diseases because they didn&#39;t live long enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156229.0,
      "end_time": 158225.0,
      "text": "to develop them."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158225.0,
      "end_time": 160338.0,
      "text": "They died of injuries --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160338.0,
      "end_time": 162823.0,
      "text": "being gored by an ox,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162823.0,
      "end_time": 164727.0,
      "text": "shot on a battlefield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 164727.0,
      "end_time": 168465.0,
      "text": "crushed in one of the new factories of the Industrial Revolution --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168465.0,
      "end_time": 171846.0,
      "text": "and most of the time from infection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171846.0,
      "end_time": 176492.0,
      "text": "which finished what those injuries began."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176492.0,
      "end_time": 180599.0,
      "text": "All of that changed when antibiotics arrived."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 180599.0,
      "end_time": 184198.0,
      "text": "Suddenly, infections that had been a death sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184198.0,
      "end_time": 187588.0,
      "text": "became something you recovered from in days."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187588.0,
      "end_time": 190630.0,
      "text": "It seemed like a miracle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190630.0,
      "end_time": 197294.0,
      "text": "and ever since, we have been living inside the golden epoch of the miracle drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197294.0,
      "end_time": 201241.0,
      "text": "And now, we are coming to an end of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201241.0,
      "end_time": 206303.0,
      "text": "My great uncle died in the last days of the pre-antibiotic era."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206303.0,
      "end_time": 211457.0,
      "text": "We stand today on the threshold of the post-antibiotic era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211457.0,
      "end_time": 215219.0,
      "text": "in the earliest days of a time when simple infections"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215219.0,
      "end_time": 220884.0,
      "text": "such as the one Joe had will kill people once again."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 220884.0,
      "end_time": 224785.0,
      "text": "In fact, they already are."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 224785.0,
      "end_time": 227618.0,
      "text": "People are dying of infections again because of a phenomenon"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 227618.0,
      "end_time": 230381.0,
      "text": "called antibiotic resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 230381.0,
      "end_time": 232119.0,
      "text": "Briefly, it works like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 232119.0,
      "end_time": 237091.0,
      "text": "Bacteria compete against each other for resources, for food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 237091.0,
      "end_time": 241758.0,
      "text": "by manufacturing lethal compounds that they direct against each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241758.0,
      "end_time": 244103.0,
      "text": "Other bacteria, to protect themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244103.0,
      "end_time": 247354.0,
      "text": "evolve defenses against that chemical attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 247354.0,
      "end_time": 249676.0,
      "text": "When we first made antibiotics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 249676.0,
      "end_time": 253878.0,
      "text": "we took those compounds into the lab and made our own versions of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 253878.0,
      "end_time": 259674.0,
      "text": "and bacteria responded to our attack the way they always had."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259673.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262097.99999999997,
      "text": "Here is what happened next:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 262098.0,
      "end_time": 265488.0,
      "text": "Penicillin was distributed in 1943,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 265488.0,
      "end_time": 270619.0,
      "text": "and widespread penicillin resistance arrived by 1945."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270619.0,
      "end_time": 273568.0,
      "text": "Vancomycin arrived in 1972,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273568.0,
      "end_time": 277028.0,
      "text": "vancomycin resistance in 1988."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 277028.0,
      "end_time": 279150.0,
      "text": "Imipenem in 1985,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 279150.0,
      "end_time": 282192.0,
      "text": "and resistance to in 1998."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 282192.0,
      "end_time": 285860.0,
      "text": "Daptomycin, one of the most recent drugs, in 2003,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285860.0,
      "end_time": 290575.0,
      "text": "and resistance to it just a year later in 2004."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 290575.0,
      "end_time": 294335.0,
      "text": "For 70 years, we played a game of leapfrog --"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 294335.0,
      "end_time": 297261.0,
      "text": "our drug and their resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297261.0,
      "end_time": 300906.0,
      "text": "and then another drug, and then resistance again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 300906.0,
      "end_time": 303437.0,
      "text": "and now the game is ending."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 303437.0,
      "end_time": 307477.0,
      "text": "Bacteria develop resistance so quickly that pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 307477.0,
      "end_time": 311842.0,
      "text": "have decided making antibiotics is not in their best interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 311842.0,
      "end_time": 314652.0,
      "text": "so there are infections moving across the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 314652.0,
      "end_time": 318111.0,
      "text": "for which, out of the more than 100 antibiotics"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 318111.0,
      "end_time": 320340.0,
      "text": "available on the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 320340.0,
      "end_time": 323754.0,
      "text": "two drugs might work with side effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 323754.0,
      "end_time": 326238.0,
      "text": "or one drug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 326238.0,
      "end_time": 328096.0,
      "text": "or none."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328096.0,
      "end_time": 330278.0,
      "text": "This is what that looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 330278.0,
      "end_time": 334458.0,
      "text": "In 2000, the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, the CDC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 334458.0,
      "end_time": 336501.0,
      "text": "identified a single case"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336501.0,
      "end_time": 338753.0,
      "text": "in a hospital in North Carolina"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 338753.0,
      "end_time": 342886.0,
      "text": "of an infection resistant to all but two drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342886.0,
      "end_time": 347205.0,
      "text": "Today, that infection, known as KPC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 347205.0,
      "end_time": 349805.0,
      "text": "has spread to every state but three,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 349805.0,
      "end_time": 352150.0,
      "text": "and to South America, Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 352150.0,
      "end_time": 354867.0,
      "text": "and the Middle East."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 354867.0,
      "end_time": 357189.0,
      "text": "In 2008, doctors in Sweden"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 357189.0,
      "end_time": 359975.0,
      "text": "diagnosed a man from India with a different infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 359975.0,
      "end_time": 363690.0,
      "text": "resistant to all but one drug that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363690.0,
      "end_time": 365919.0,
      "text": "The gene that creates that resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365919.0,
      "end_time": 372444.0,
      "text": "known as NDM, has now spread from India into China, Asia, Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 372444.0,
      "end_time": 377129.0,
      "text": "Europe and Canada, and the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377129.0,
      "end_time": 379688.0,
      "text": "It would be natural to hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 379688.0,
      "end_time": 383287.0,
      "text": "that these infections are extraordinary cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 383287.0,
      "end_time": 385145.0,
      "text": "but in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385145.0,
      "end_time": 387606.0,
      "text": "in the United States and Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 387606.0,
      "end_time": 390322.0,
      "text": "50,000 people a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 390322.0,
      "end_time": 394966.0,
      "text": "die of infections which no drugs can help."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 394966.0,
      "end_time": 398008.0,
      "text": "A project chartered by the British government"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398008.0,
      "end_time": 401746.0,
      "text": "known as the Review on Antimicrobial Resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 401746.0,
      "end_time": 410291.0,
      "text": "estimates that the worldwide toll right now is 700,000 deaths a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 410291.0,
      "end_time": 414655.0,
      "text": "That is a lot of deaths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 414655.0,
      "end_time": 417767.0,
      "text": "and yet, the chances are good that you don&#39;t feel at risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 417767.0,
      "end_time": 420995.0,
      "text": "that you imagine these people were hospital patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 420995.0,
      "end_time": 422713.0,
      "text": "in intensive care units"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 422713.0,
      "end_time": 426660.0,
      "text": "or nursing home residents near the ends of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 426660.0,
      "end_time": 429841.0,
      "text": "people whose infections are remote from us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429841.0,
      "end_time": 434455.0,
      "text": "in situations we can&#39;t identify with."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 434455.0,
      "end_time": 437852.0,
      "text": "What you didn&#39;t think about, none of us do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 437852.0,
      "end_time": 443721.0,
      "text": "is that antibiotics support almost all of modern life."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 443721.0,
      "end_time": 445932.0,
      "text": "If we lost antibiotics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 445932.0,
      "end_time": 447836.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s what else we&#39;d lose:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 447836.0,
      "end_time": 452015.0,
      "text": "First, any protection for people with weakened immune systems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 452015.0,
      "end_time": 455475.0,
      "text": "cancer patients, AIDS patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 455475.0,
      "end_time": 459979.0,
      "text": "transplant recipients, premature babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 459979.0,
      "end_time": 464391.0,
      "text": "Next, any treatment that installs foreign objects in the body:"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 464391.0,
      "end_time": 468269.0,
      "text": "stents for stroke, pumps for diabetes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 468269.0,
      "end_time": 472193.0,
      "text": "dialysis, joint replacements."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 472193.0,
      "end_time": 475908.0,
      "text": "How many athletic baby boomers need new hips and knees?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 475908.0,
      "end_time": 478717.0,
      "text": "A recent study estimates that without antibiotics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 478717.0,
      "end_time": 482664.0,
      "text": "one out of ever six would die."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 482664.0,
      "end_time": 485869.0,
      "text": "Next, we&#39;d probably lose surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 485869.0,
      "end_time": 488191.0,
      "text": "Many operations are preceded"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 488191.0,
      "end_time": 491139.0,
      "text": "by prophylactic doses of antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 491139.0,
      "end_time": 492811.0,
      "text": "Without that protection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 492811.0,
      "end_time": 497015.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d lose the ability to open the hidden spaces of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 497015.0,
      "end_time": 499848.0,
      "text": "So no heart operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 499848.0,
      "end_time": 502680.0,
      "text": "no prostate biopsies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 502680.0,
      "end_time": 505792.0,
      "text": "no Cesarean sections."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 505792.0,
      "end_time": 510784.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d have to learn to fear infections that now seem minor."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 510784.0,
      "end_time": 514592.0,
      "text": "Strep throat used to cause heart failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 514592.0,
      "end_time": 517819.0,
      "text": "Skin infections led to amputations."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 517818.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520721.99999999994,
      "text": "Giving birth killed, in the cleanest hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 520722.0,
      "end_time": 523717.0,
      "text": "almost one woman out of every 100."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 523717.0,
      "end_time": 529220.0,
      "text": "Pneumonia took three children out of every 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 529220.0,
      "end_time": 531333.0,
      "text": "More than anything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 531333.0,
      "end_time": 536836.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d lose the confident way we live our everyday lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 536836.0,
      "end_time": 541043.0,
      "text": "If you knew that any injury could kill you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 541043.0,
      "end_time": 544289.0,
      "text": "would you ride a motorcycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 544289.0,
      "end_time": 547500.0,
      "text": "bomb down a ski slope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 547500.0,
      "end_time": 550976.0,
      "text": "climb a ladder to hang your Christmas lights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 550976.0,
      "end_time": 555573.0,
      "text": "let your kid slide into home plate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 555573.0,
      "end_time": 558638.0,
      "text": "After all, the first person to receive penicillin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 558638.0,
      "end_time": 562516.0,
      "text": "a British policeman named Albert Alexander,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 562516.0,
      "end_time": 566858.0,
      "text": "who was so ravaged by infection that his scalp oozed pus"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 566858.0,
      "end_time": 569783.0,
      "text": "and doctors had to take out an eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 569783.0,
      "end_time": 574172.0,
      "text": "was infected by doing something very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 574172.0,
      "end_time": 580831.0,
      "text": "He walked into his garden and scratched his face on a thorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 580831.0,
      "end_time": 584481.0,
      "text": "That British project I mentioned which estimates that the worldwide toll"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 584481.0,
      "end_time": 588358.0,
      "text": "right now is 700,000 deaths a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 588358.0,
      "end_time": 594535.0,
      "text": "also predicts that if we can&#39;t get this under control by 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 594535.0,
      "end_time": 602127.0,
      "text": "not long, the worldwide toll will be 10 million deaths a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 602127.0,
      "end_time": 604829.0,
      "text": "How did we get to this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 604829.0,
      "end_time": 606864.0,
      "text": "where what we have to look forward to"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 606864.0,
      "end_time": 610347.0,
      "text": "is those terrifying numbers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 610347.0,
      "end_time": 614875.0,
      "text": "The difficult answer is, we did it to ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 614875.0,
      "end_time": 617847.0,
      "text": "Resistance is an inevitable biological process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 617847.0,
      "end_time": 622490.0,
      "text": "but we bear the responsibility for accelerating it."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 622490.0,
      "end_time": 626043.0,
      "text": "We did this by squandering antibiotics"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 626043.0,
      "end_time": 631408.0,
      "text": "with a heedlessness that now seems shocking."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 631408.0,
      "end_time": 635494.0,
      "text": "Penicillin was sold over the counter until the 1950s."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 635494.0,
      "end_time": 639209.0,
      "text": "In much of the developing world, most antibiotics still are."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 639209.0,
      "end_time": 642971.0,
      "text": "In the United States, 50 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 642971.0,
      "end_time": 646663.0,
      "text": "of the antibiotics given in hospitals are unnecessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 646663.0,
      "end_time": 651037.0,
      "text": "Forty-five percent of the prescriptions written in doctor&#39;s offices"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 651037.0,
      "end_time": 656577.0,
      "text": "are for conditions that antibiotics cannot help."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 656577.0,
      "end_time": 659247.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s just in healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 659247.0,
      "end_time": 664100.0,
      "text": "On much of the planet, most meat animals get antibiotics every day of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 664100.0,
      "end_time": 666376.0,
      "text": "not to cure illnesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 666376.0,
      "end_time": 669835.0,
      "text": "but to fatten them up and to protect them against"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 669835.0,
      "end_time": 673806.0,
      "text": "the factory farm conditions they are raised in."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 673806.0,
      "end_time": 676824.0,
      "text": "In the United States, possibly 80 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 676824.0,
      "end_time": 683527.0,
      "text": "of the antibiotics sold every year go to farm animals, not to humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 683527.0,
      "end_time": 687203.0,
      "text": "creating resistant bacteria that move off the farm"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 687203.0,
      "end_time": 689827.0,
      "text": "in water, in dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 689827.0,
      "end_time": 692985.0,
      "text": "in the meat the animals become."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 692985.0,
      "end_time": 695910.0,
      "text": "Aquaculture depends on antibiotics too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 695910.0,
      "end_time": 697559.0,
      "text": "particularly in Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 697559.0,
      "end_time": 700902.0,
      "text": "and fruit growing relies on antibiotics"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 700902.0,
      "end_time": 706491.0,
      "text": "to protect apples, pears, citrus, against disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 706491.0,
      "end_time": 712117.0,
      "text": "And because bacteria can pass their DNA to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 712117.0,
      "end_time": 716552.0,
      "text": "like a traveler handing off a suitcase at an airport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 716552.0,
      "end_time": 721360.0,
      "text": "once we have encouraged that resistance into existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 721360.0,
      "end_time": 725723.0,
      "text": "there is no knowing where it will spread."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 725723.0,
      "end_time": 727674.0,
      "text": "This was predictable."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 727674.0,
      "end_time": 730506.0,
      "text": "In fact, it was predicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 730506.0,
      "end_time": 734941.0,
      "text": "by Alexander Fleming, the man who discovered penicillin."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 734941.0,
      "end_time": 738935.0,
      "text": "He was given the Nobel Prize in 1945 in recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 738935.0,
      "end_time": 743282.0,
      "text": "and in an interview shortly after, this is what he said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 743282.0,
      "end_time": 747549.0,
      "text": "&quot;The thoughtless person playing with penicillin treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 747549.0,
      "end_time": 750823.0,
      "text": "is morally responsible for the death of a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 750823.0,
      "end_time": 753147.0,
      "text": "who succumbs to infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 753147.0,
      "end_time": 756050.0,
      "text": "with a pencillin-resistant organism.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 756050.0,
      "end_time": 760986.0,
      "text": "He added, &quot;I hope this evil can be averted.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 760986.0,
      "end_time": 763842.0,
      "text": "Can we avert it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 763842.0,
      "end_time": 767510.0,
      "text": "There are companies working on novel antibiotics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 767510.0,
      "end_time": 771086.0,
      "text": "things the superbugs have never seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 771086.0,
      "end_time": 773803.0,
      "text": "We need those new drugs badly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 773803.0,
      "end_time": 776055.0,
      "text": "and we need incentives:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 776055.0,
      "end_time": 778586.0,
      "text": "discovery grants, extended patents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 778586.0,
      "end_time": 785343.0,
      "text": "prizes, to lure other companies into making antibiotics again."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 785343.0,
      "end_time": 788059.0,
      "text": "But that probably won&#39;t be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 788059.0,
      "end_time": 792703.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s why: Evolution always wins."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 792703.0,
      "end_time": 796627.0,
      "text": "Bacteria birth a new generation every 20 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 796627.0,
      "end_time": 801410.0,
      "text": "It takes pharmaceutical chemistry 10 years to derive a new drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 801410.0,
      "end_time": 804266.0,
      "text": "Every time we use an antibiotic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 804266.0,
      "end_time": 807540.0,
      "text": "we give the bacteria billions of chances"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 807540.0,
      "end_time": 809281.0,
      "text": "to crack the codes"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 809281.0,
      "end_time": 812486.0,
      "text": "of the defenses we&#39;ve constructed."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 812486.0,
      "end_time": 814877.0,
      "text": "There has never yet been a drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 814877.0,
      "end_time": 817431.0,
      "text": "they could not defeat."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 817431.0,
      "end_time": 820961.0,
      "text": "This is asymmetric warfare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 820961.0,
      "end_time": 825929.0,
      "text": "but we can change the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 825929.0,
      "end_time": 832334.0,
      "text": "We could build systems to harvest data to tell us automatically and specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 832334.0,
      "end_time": 835263.0,
      "text": "how antibiotics are being used."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 835263.0,
      "end_time": 838096.0,
      "text": "We could build gatekeeping into drug order systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 838096.0,
      "end_time": 841811.0,
      "text": "so that every prescription gets a second look."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 841811.0,
      "end_time": 848243.0,
      "text": "We could require agriculture to give up antibiotic use."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 848243.0,
      "end_time": 851275.0,
      "text": "We could build surveillance systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 851275.0,
      "end_time": 855501.0,
      "text": "to tell us where resistance is emerging next."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 855501.0,
      "end_time": 858264.0,
      "text": "Those are the tech solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 858264.0,
      "end_time": 860888.0,
      "text": "They probably aren&#39;t enough either,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 860888.0,
      "end_time": 867785.0,
      "text": "unless we help."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 867785.0,
      "end_time": 870479.0,
      "text": "Antibiotic resistance is a habit."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 870479.0,
      "end_time": 873567.0,
      "text": "We all know how hard it is to change a habit."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 873567.0,
      "end_time": 878397.0,
      "text": "But as a society, we&#39;ve done that in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 878397.0,
      "end_time": 881972.0,
      "text": "People used to toss litter into the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 881972.0,
      "end_time": 883737.0,
      "text": "used to not wear seatbelts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 883737.0,
      "end_time": 888404.0,
      "text": "used to smoke inside public buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 888404.0,
      "end_time": 891144.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t do those things anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 891144.0,
      "end_time": 893466.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t trash the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 893466.0,
      "end_time": 896623.0,
      "text": "or court devastating accidents"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 896623.0,
      "end_time": 899595.0,
      "text": "or expose others to the possibility of cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 899595.0,
      "end_time": 903102.0,
      "text": "because we decided those things were expensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 903102.0,
      "end_time": 907815.0,
      "text": "destructive, not in our best interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 907815.0,
      "end_time": 911135.0,
      "text": "We changed social norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 911135.0,
      "end_time": 917499.0,
      "text": "We could change social norms around antibiotic use too."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 917499.0,
      "end_time": 919774.0,
      "text": "I know that the scale of antibiotic resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 919774.0,
      "end_time": 921678.0,
      "text": "seems overwhelming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 921678.0,
      "end_time": 925138.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;ve ever bought a fluorescent lightbulb"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 925138.0,
      "end_time": 927854.0,
      "text": "because you were concerned about climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 927854.0,
      "end_time": 930989.0,
      "text": "or read the label on a box of crackers"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 930989.0,
      "end_time": 935470.0,
      "text": "because you think about the deforestation from palm oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 935470.0,
      "end_time": 938349.0,
      "text": "you already know what it feels like"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 938349.0,
      "end_time": 943829.0,
      "text": "to take a tiny step to address an overwhelming problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 943829.0,
      "end_time": 948310.0,
      "text": "We could take those kinds of steps for antibiotic use too."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 948310.0,
      "end_time": 956251.0,
      "text": "We could forgo giving an antibiotic if we&#39;re not sure it&#39;s the right one."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 956251.0,
      "end_time": 962564.0,
      "text": "We could stop insisting on a prescription for our kid&#39;s ear infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 962564.0,
      "end_time": 965678.0,
      "text": "before we&#39;re sure what caused it."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 965678.0,
      "end_time": 969045.0,
      "text": "We could ask every restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 969045.0,
      "end_time": 970856.0,
      "text": "every supermarket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 970856.0,
      "end_time": 972806.0,
      "text": "where their meat comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 972806.0,
      "end_time": 974640.0,
      "text": "We could promise each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 974640.0,
      "end_time": 978745.0,
      "text": "never again to buy chicken or shrimp or fruit"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 978745.0,
      "end_time": 981629.0,
      "text": "raised with routine antibiotic use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 981629.0,
      "end_time": 984323.0,
      "text": "and if we did those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 984323.0,
      "end_time": 989547.0,
      "text": "we could slow down the arrival of the post-antibiotic world."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 989547.0,
      "end_time": 993680.0,
      "text": "But we have to do it soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 993680.0,
      "end_time": 998185.0,
      "text": "Penicillin began the antibiotic era in 1943."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 998185.0,
      "end_time": 1004291.0,
      "text": "In just 70 years, we walked ourselves up to the edge of disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1004290.0,
      "end_time": 1006612.0,
      "text": "We won&#39;t get 70 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1006610.0,
      "end_time": 1010766.0,
      "text": "to find our way back out again."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1010770.0,
      "end_time": 1012790.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1012790.0,
      "end_time": 1022790.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}